      <title>中国央行加强对经济短期困境的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-central-bank-sharpens-focus-on-economy-s-short-term-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行誓言要从现有的促增长政策中获得更多收益，并承认尽管今年出现了一些改善的迹象，但经济仍受到需求疲软和悲观情绪的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-central-bank-sharpens-focus-on-economy-s-short-term-woes</guid>
